title: Episode 8 - Where is oil headed?
itunes:title: Where is oil headed?
description:
Frank
talks to Phil Flynn and Matt Badiali - two of the top oil analysts on Wall
Street. One predicts $150 oil in 2010. The other suggests oil could fall if the
Fed begins to tighten.
